The paper proposes a deep learning algorithm for mapping solar PV arrays in high resolution overhead imagery, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The algorithm also involves training a neural network, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the deployment of the algorithm to new geographic regions, which could fall under the sub-categories of graphics (cs.GR) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
